officers.name: Ben Wong
officers.title: Banquet Coordinator, Events Coordinator Co-chair
officers.bio: Ben helps make tech talks and infosessions, and other miscellaneous IEEE events happen. He also helps plan the EE department banquet coming in Spring.

officers.name: Dillon Tellier
officers.title: Branch President
officers.bio: As Chair of the Cal Poly IEEE Student Branch, Dillon oversees all IEEE operations and maintains crucial relations between the department and the club all while helping steer IEEE towards further success.

officers.name: Tannis Hodge
officers.title: Branch President
officers.bio: I make sure the club runs smoothy and autonomously.

officers.name: Benjamin Lin
officers.title: Internal Vice President
officers.bio: Benjamin Lin is enjoys anything DSP related. He is currently taking Computer Vision and Digital Signal Processing. Talk to Benjamin if you want a quick chat.

officers.name: Tyler Kowallis
officers.title: Liaison
officers.bio: Tyler handles all inter-club correspondence. He is interested in all things digital, philosophical, and Japanese.

officers.name: David Ritter
officers.title: Parts Coordinator
officers.bio: David orders all the parts and make the labkits. Let him know if the shop is out parts and he\u0027ll do what he can.

officers.name: Alfredo Sanchez
officers.title: Project Manager
officers.bio: Alfredo can frequently be spotted in the IEEE Lab with fellow classmates working on assignments or socializing. In his spare time he enjoys rock climbing and light runs around town. Alfredo is very approachable and open to meeting new people and making friends.

officers.name: Kelli De Vlugt
officers.title: Publicity Manager
officers.bio: Kelli is the mastermind behind all graphic publications for IEEE.

officers.name: Rebecca Krieger
officers.title: Resource Manager
officers.bio: Rebecca is an Electrical Engineer considering switching to SE and double majoring in Psych. She is interested in artificial intelligence.

officers.name: Jessica Nguyen
officers.title: Secretary
officers.bio: Hi everyone! I\u0027m a second year at Cal Poly. My hometown is Stockton located in California\u0027s central valley. In my free time I like hiking, painting, drawing, photography and journalism.

officers.name: Billy Luo
officers.title: Treasurer
officers.bio: Billy is a 3rd year CPE who is pursuing Cal Poly\u0027s 4+1 EE master\u0027s program. He plans on focusing in analog electronics and embedded systems.

officers.name: Jacob Hladky
officers.title: Treasurer
officers.bio: Jacob is an aspiring low-level developer and systems programmer. He enjoys FPGAs and microcontrollers.

officers.name: David Zhuo
officers.title: Vice President External
officers.bio: David helps make tech talks, info sessions, and other IEEE events happen.

officers.name: Taylor McClain
officers.title: Vice President External
officers.bio: Taylor makes sure that everyone does their job and isn\u0027t afraid to raise his voice if he has to. From babysitting the other officers to coordinating all things outside of the school that IEEE is involved with; Taylor does it all.

officers.name: Angela Yoeurng
officers.title: Vice President External
officers.bio: Angela\u0027s in charge of overseeing all IEEE\u0027s external communication and making sure the club doesn\u0027t go boom. Angela can often be found in the ICL (20-115), so stop by and say hi!

officers.name: Andrew Ma
officers.title: Workshop Coordinator
officers.bio: Andrew is one of the workshop coordinators for 2013-2014. Look forward to the CMOY project he is putting together this winter quarter!

officers.name: Oleg Frandle
officers.title: Workshop Coordinator
officers.bio: Oleg is tasked with designing and organizing workshops throughout the year that are fun and applicable. If you have any ideas or suggestions for workshops you would like to see happen, feel free to send him an email!

officers.name: Traci Takasugi
officers.title: Workshop Coordinator
officers.bio: Physics minor and facilitator of student workshops.
